stimulusHtml: According to lines 1-2 (At . . . haesit), what is one physical effect of Aeneasâ€™ reaction? Write out the Latin to support your answer.

features.html:
At vero Aeneas aspectu obmutuit amens,

              arrectaeque horrore comae et vox faucibus haesit.

    Ardet abire fuga dulcesque relinquere terras,

attonitus tanto monitu imperioque deorum.

                        (5) Heu quid agat? Quo nunc reginam ambire furentem

 audeat adfatu? Quae prima exordia sumat?

Aeneid 4.279-284
